{"tid":1049752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"救命 老母中投資騙局","createTime":"2019-03-06T13:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T14:27:21.000Z","uid":240868,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"731f527247846fafde82a69492f970db6fc0ef56","tid":1049752,"uid":240868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我老母有日俾人拉左返大陸<br />\n應該係聽左d投資講座<br />\n返到來同我老豆講d發達大計<br />\n<br />\n內容大概係有間電梯公司<br />\n間公司好大 好靚 好巴閉 <br />\n有好多專家 申請左好多專利 <br />\n中央台吹捧 連雜總都支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n準備係美國上市<br />\n又有個咩總投資左百鳩幾萬<br />\n識人先俾佢投資埋一份<br />\n<br />\n好啦 咁大隻蛤乸 佛都心動<br />\n聽到都扯扯地 扯火嗰隻扯<br />\n<br />\n我同佢講係呃鳩人 <br />\n咩係龐氐騙局都講埋<br />\n佢俾人洗腦洗到屌返我轉頭<br />\n前前後後已經嘈左幾穫金<br />\n嘈到隔離屋要報警嗰隻<br />\n暫時知佢&ldquo;投資&rdquo;左幾皮野<br />\n<br />\n今晚又嘈完 我嬲到走左出街<br />\n宜家公園吹緊風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走嗰陣佢屌我老豆做乜話我知佢&ldquo;投資&ldquo;<br />\n其實佢地係廳大大聲講<br />\n我自己係房己聽到<br />\n<br />\nbtw好撚凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4390d871dd3b25610f866327459f40b532f074","tid":1049752,"uid":188155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01fe7bb4e80ad8607bfb2f5c2f655e8fc10e74d4","tid":1049752,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:29:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6be641bd3aa97a81f1be9b9e248c2100e16a6e18","tid":1049752,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e5bba97f2966aaa2e101c106a0c677327ad23dc","tid":1049752,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9e021375a62ab3c4acc84741e22b103e16541d2","tid":1049752,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"唔死都冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" cla